## Root layout (non-service paths)

| Path | Role / when editing |
|------|---------------------|
| **`doc/`** | Human-oriented docs |
| **`.cursor/rules/`** | Repo-wide pointers (this tree) |
| **`infra/aws_tf/`** | **Only** `terraform init/plan/apply` root |
| **`infra/deployed/aws/.../services/<svc>/`** | Ownership markers + Helm—not a TF root |
| **`infra/tf_lib/`** | Read-only TF snippets; skills copy into **`infra/aws_tf/modules/`** |
| **`.cursor/skills/`**, **`aspire.svc/.cursor/skills/`** | Root IaC skills; **`aspire-registry-tool`** only under aspire.svc |
| **`AGENTS.md`**, **`CLAUDE.md`** | Optional repo-wide agent hints |

Apps and microservices: see **Solution components** table above. Per-service rules: **`iam.svc/.cursor/rules/`**, **`solutions.svc/.cursor/rules/`** (`microservice`, `architetcure`, `validation`, `database`, `logging`, `grpc`); AWS via root **`infra.mdc`** / **`terrafrom.mdc`**.

## AWS / Terraform (all paths)

Follow **`infra.mdc`**, **`terrafrom.mdc`**, **`.cursor/skills/`**. Never re-declare account, profile, region, or **`PROJECT_*`** outside **`constants.mdc`**. Runnable TF only in **`infra/aws_tf/`**; markers and Helm in **`infra/deployed/`**.
